stateDiagram
  direction LR
  classDef boot fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#856404,stroke-width:2px;
  classDef run fill:#d1e7dd,stroke:#198754,stroke-width:2px;
  classDef vector fill:#f0f4ff,stroke:#4c6ef5,stroke-width:2px;
  classDef handle fill:#e7f5ff,stroke:#0d6efd,stroke-width:2px;
  classDef fatal fill:#f8d7da,stroke:#dc3545,stroke-width:2px;
  state Boot {
    direction TB
    [*] --> Entry
    Entry --> Early
    Early --> Init
[*]    Entry
    Early
    Init
  }
  state SteadyState {
    direction TB
    [*] --> Loop
[*]    Loop
  }
  state Vector {
    direction TB
    Dispatch
  }
  state Handling {
    direction TB
    state Sync {
      direction TB
      Exception
    }
    state Async {
      direction TB
      Interrupt
    }
  }
  Boot --> SteadyState:Boot Complete
  SteadyState --> Vector:Trap / IRQ
  Vector --> Exception:Vector entry
  Vector --> Interrupt:Vector entry
  Exception --> SteadyState:Return (MOVS PC, LR)
  Interrupt --> SteadyState:Return (SUBS PC, LR, #4)
  Exception --> Halt:Fatal Error
  Boot:1. BOOT SEQUENCE
  Entry:<b>_start</b><br>(Entry Point)
  Early:<b>Early Phase</b><br>(Minimal Env)
  Init:<b>Init Phase</b><br>(Setup VBAR)
  SteadyState:2. STEADY STATE
  Loop:<b>Kernel Main Loop</b><br/>(Shell Event Loop)
  Vector:3. VECTOR TABLE
  Dispatch:<b>Vector Dispatch</b><br>(VBAR + offset)
  Handling:4. EVENT HANDLING (Privileged)
  Sync:Synchronous
  Exception:<b>EXCEPTION</b><br>(Undef, SVC, Abort)
  Async:Asynchronous
  Interrupt:<b>INTERRUPT</b><br>(IRQ, FIQ)
  Halt:System Halt
  class Boot boot
  class SteadyState run
  class Vector vector
  class Handling handle
  class Halt fatal